   .                   \\ /\ //|| ||\\|| ||  )                      .
   .                    \V/\V/ || || \|| ||_//                      .
   .                  =========================                     .
   . input port       |    USE    |  PROVIDE  |                     .
   .____________      |...........|...........|                     .
   .|self-input| -->  | input     | wind-velo |                     .
   .------------      |...........|...........|                     .
   . provide-like     | spat.-pos.| state     |       output port   .
   .                  |...........|...........|     _____________   .
   .                  |           | output    | --> |self-output|   .
   .                  =========================     -------------   .
